				<div class="postbody">
				I'm currently developing for a company that sells an IT Management product called EM7. <a href="http://www.sciencelogic.com" target="_blank" class="postlink">www.sciencelogic.com</a>
<br />

<br />
We're pretty new as a company, but the product has been in development for a long time.
<br />

<br />
Pros: It's one of the most robust management platforms out there, and much cheaper than anything comparable. It's an appliance, meaning it comes bundled software/server together. It does everything.
<br />

<br />
Cons: Not free. Not open source. If anyone is seriously interested, send me a pm and I'll see if I can hook up a demo for you.
<br />

<br />
Here's a couple cool screenshots:
<br />

<br />

